short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Check your Discord tokens and login

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is a Chrome extension for Discord tokens checking and login. This tool allows you to quickly login with user tokens in your browser without having to enter a script into the console every time.
